cs.LO, cs.PL, cs.CC, cs.DS, cs.AI 

Reasoning: 
- cs.LO (Logic in Computer Science) is the most likely category as the paper is about a new deductive system for logic and its application in arithmetic. 
- cs.PL (Programming Languages) is also likely as the paper discusses a new program for redeveloping logic as a formal theory of computability. 
- cs.CC (Computational Complexity) is relevant as the paper deals with the computational aspects of logic and the complexity of solving computational problems. 
- cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) is relevant as the paper discusses the representation of computational problems as formulas and the encoding of solutions as proofs. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is relevant as the paper discusses the use of logic as a basis for applied theories, which could have implications for AI.
